{"tid":1533733,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱開始打香城online 求裝備攻略","createTime":"2019-09-02T20:04:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T17:46:18.000Z","uid":259557,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"068cc7a414646ff9b2238b70d8de2fd2bd12851d","tid":1533733,"uid":259557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T20:04:19.000Z","msg":"我係香城online新手，之前一路都係睇人直播打呢隻game，但係見住愈嚟愈多玩家受傷，冇得落場玩，覺得再咁落去唔係辦法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n9月2都去咗中大罷課，出過一次機場之後感受真係好唔同<br />\n我諗我之後都會成日on呢隻game，例如9月8一定出<br />\n<br />\n但係我預咗自己暫時唔會上前線，入黑後會早走<br />\n（我絲，體能唔好，跑得慢，留到太夜/係前線只會連累前線手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n想問我宜家應該買咩裝備好？要買到幾高level嘅裝備先夠用？<br />\n有啲驚帶住裝到現場時比狗查袋會出事，但唔買裝又好似太危險<br />\n<br />\n對唔住 我都唔想做伸手黨，但係身邊一個會玩香城online嘅人都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好無助 唯有上嚟問下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n順便問多句，有冇絲都係會單機出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己冇乜朋友搵唔到隊友一齊出<br />\n<br />\nSorry for咁遲先開始玩，我都知自己衰，好後悔冇早啲加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對唔住大家<br />\n<br />\n都Sorry for P牌，有咗大學email成年，但係之前覺得冇必要開ac所以一直冇開，係6月為咗睇發夢資訊先開嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b734099b27471beb8509a355020ba27d384901df","tid":1533733,"uid":259557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T20:04:42.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03dbadbf20af7096382e41ee98ffc333d5fe0cba","tid":1533733,"uid":38610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T20:06:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"210ede756822366e378272deaef4e00a738fedf5","tid":1533733,"uid":2904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T20:07:34.000Z"